    dc:description "FIGURES 21–27. Aulocera spp., (left) upperside, (right) underside. 21. A. pumilus, ♂, Kaschmir, Marsimik Pass, illustrated by Gross (1959: pl. I: 5), Lep153401, ZFMK; 22. ditto, ♀, Kaschmir, Shigar River, illustrated by Gross (1959: pl. I: 6), Lep153405, ZFMK; 23. A. iole, ♂, Sichuan, Kangding, ANDR0138, SATY0041, LSY; 24. ditto, ♀, Sichuan, Kangding, SATY0778, LSY; 25. A. sybillina spp. incert., ♂, Gansu, Peilingshan, Lep153511, ZFMK; 26. A. sybillina sybillina, ♂, Ta-tsien-lou (Sichuan, Kangding), Lep153407, ZFMK; 27. A. sybillina bianor, ♂, Kuku nor Thibet sept. or (Qinghai), illustrated by Gross (1959: pl. II: 4), Lep153408, ZFMK." ;
